        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ʲo��SHELL"><a href="#ʲo��SHELL" class="headerlink" title="ʲô��SHELL"></a>ʲô��SHELL</h1><p>Linux����ϵͳ�ǰ�װ��Ӳ��֮ǰ����Ӳ���Ĳ�����Ҫͨ������ϵͳ����ô���Բ���ϵͳ��ʹ�������������в�������windons�Ĳ���һ������linux��Ϊһ��������Ĳ���ϵͳ��һ�㰲װ�ڷ������ϣ��û�ͨ��Զ�����Ӻ�ʹ�ã�ͨ��ʹ�����ʽ������ʹ��linuxϵͳ�������е���ڼ���shell��shell������windowns�µ�cmd��powershell������ϵͳ���û����棬�ṩ���û����ں˽��н���������һ�ֽӿڡ��������û������������������ں�ȥִ�С�</p><p>��ñ��ҵLnux��Ϊ�û��ṩ��Ĭ��shell�� GNU Bourne-Again Shell��bash����Bash����UNIX���Ƶ�ϵͳ��ʹ�õ�����һ����ɹ�she�ĸĽ��汾���� Bourne shel1��sh��������bash��ϵͳ���ṩ������shell:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@node03 ~]# cat &#x2F;etc&#x2F;shells </span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;sh</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;sbin&#x2F;nologin</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;dash</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;tcsh</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;csh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="shell��ʾ��"><a href="#shell��ʾ��" class="headerlink" title="shell��ʾ��"></a>shell��ʾ��</h1><h2 id="I����ʾ��"><a href="#I����ʾ��" class="headerlink" title="Ĭ����ʾ��"></a>Ĭ����ʾ��</h2><p>Ϊ������root�û����root�û���shell��ʾ��Ĭ���ǲ�һ���ġ�</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ROOT�û�</span><br><span class="line">[root@node03 ~]# </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">��root�û�</spa